Package net.sourceforge.jpalm.palmdb

This package is for reading and writing Palm database files. This work is based upon:
  • open source projects related to Palm databases
  • DataMgr.h, found in the Palm OS SDK
  • the Palm API Reference
See the resources folder bundled with the distribution.
Example Code: Creating a PalmDB Database, Reading a PalmDB Database

    Interface Description
    PalmDB
